{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require Members of Parliament to have min 15yrs work experience outside politics",
        "additional_details": "Anyone sitting in parliament should have a minimum of 15 years PAYE outside of politics\r\n \r\nWe feel career politicians cannot truly comprehend and manage something they may have no real world experience of.\r\n \r\nMuch like someone studying very hard for many years academically then being let loose as a brain surgeon!",
        "background": "Ensure the elected representatives of the people have the relevant real world experience necessary to make more informed decisions.",
